{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, users can modify and export the generated codes, which providing flexibility for those who need to customize their analyses further.Task flow view: The task flow view updates as goals and tasks are added, providing the user with a clear analysis of status and progress (Fig. 4C).",
    "Each node is a rectangular box showing the task id, task type, and percent progress.",
    "The original task text appears when the cursor is over a node.",
    "Clicking on a node will update the visualization layout in the Visualization view.",
    "Hovering over the edge can see the differences in data and task type between the associated nodes."
  ]
}